<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. كُلُّ امْرِئٍ مِنْهُمْ يُعْطَى قُوَى مائَةً<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>فِي الأَكْلِ وَالشُّرْبِ وَالإِفْضَا بِلا خَوَرِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>طَعَامُهُمْ رَشْحُ مِسْكٍ كُلَّمَا عَرِقُوا<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>عَادَتْ بُطُونُهُمْ فِي هَضْمِ مُنْضَمِرِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>لا جُوعَ لا بَرْدَ لا هَمٌ وَلا نَصَبٌ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>بَلْ عَيْشُهُمْ عَنْ جَمِيعِ النَّائِبَاتِ عَرِي<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>فِيهَا الْوَصَائِفُ وَالْغُلْمَانُ تَخْدُمُهُمْ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>كَلُؤْلُؤ فِي كَمَالِ الْحُسْنِ مُنْتَثِرِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>فِيهَا الْغِنَا وَالْجَوَارِي الْغَانِيَاتُ لَهُمْ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>بِأَحْسَنِ الذِّكْرِ لِلْمَوْلَى مَعَ السَّمَرِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>لِبَاسُهُمْ سُنْدُسٌ حُلاهُمْ ذَهَبٌ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>وَلُؤْلُؤٌ وَنَعِيمٌ غَيْرُ مُنْحَصِرِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَالذِّكْرُ كَالنَّفَسِ الْجَارِي بِلا تَعَبٍ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>وَنُزِّهُوا عَنْ كَلامَ اللَّغْوِ وَالْهَذَرِ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>وَأَكْلُهَا دَائِمٌ لا شَيْءَ مُنْقَطِعٌ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>كَرِّرْ أَحَادِيثَهَا فِي أَطْيَبِ الْخَبَرِ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>فِيهَا مِنَ الْخَيْرِ مَا لَمْ يَجْرِي فِي خَلَدٍ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>وَلَمْ يَكُنْ مُدْرِكًا لِلسَّمْعِ وَالْبَصَرِ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>فِيهَا رِضَا الْمَلِكَ الْمَوْلَى بِلا غَضَبٍ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>سُبْحَانَهُ وَلَهُمْ نَفْعٌ بِلا غِيَرِ ... &gt;?<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>